Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看不到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们的眼中  我们是公司的干部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用Di-Sword造出粒子  注入周围的人的盲点中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,giga-lo-maniacs可是很厉害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过绝不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜  那个人  西条拓巳…必须要将他铲除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我…动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  他还有必须要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得做过的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我可是马上就忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人可以做到有人做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的人一定很浪漫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常做很长很长的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经也是  有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是幻觉  心中的泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得快点醒来  不然的话  终有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会被西条拓巳所消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我也不后悔  这个梦终有一天要终结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦终结之后…还能剩下什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来Noah2也不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到地下后职员都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…或许是下班了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noah2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你们想要的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOZOMI科技社长  野吕濑玄一！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来访  giga-lo-maniacs少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就被识破身份了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中埋伏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量体温的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说有一位拿着剑的少女到处攻击我们公司的Porter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就猜到是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波多野濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波多野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名不是姓苍井的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们两人竟然认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太擅长这种用剑来相互争斗的野蛮行为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Di-Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野吕濑也是giga-lo-maniacs吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥格斗游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到父亲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻击都被看穿了  为什么
