Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好怕的
