Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了粉碎你的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了一件绝妙的玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名
