Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视觉投影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五感控制
